1a. PLATFORM REPOSITORY & FORKING RESTRICTION
─────────────────────────────────────────────

Forking, cloning, mirroring, or otherwise creating copies of any
TrafkHop Entertainment™ repository on GitHub, GitLab, Codeberg, or any
other code hosting or version control platform is strictly prohibited
without explicit written permission.

If a fork or clone is created solely for the purpose of submitting a pull
request or contribution, such fork must be deleted immediately after the
corresponding pull request is closed or merged.

Automated mirroring, scraping, or archiving of repositories — whether by
bots, scripts, or platform features — is prohibited without prior written
consent.

